      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I could respect the fact of getting hit, getting hit in the ribs or the body. I know that's part of the game, I accept that and I don't have any problem with that. But I feel there's a difference between that and almost ending my career.''</p>
        <p>MIKE PIAZZA, on being hit in the head by a fastball from Roger Clemens. [D1]</p>
